{
  "title": "Darkly Savory Argentinian Sausages Skewers",
  "description": "A tangy and crumbly Argentinian dish featuring German sausages, dashi extract, and plant-based friendly ingredients, perfect for a midnight craving. This recipe combines the flavors of Argentina and Germany with a Japanese twist.",
  "cuisine": "Argentinian",
